Operation Sticky Gate

Mojisoluwa (Jiso) Awe

What is Operation Sticky Gate?

Major League Baseball’s 2021 season has been marked by record breaking statistics. Particularly the record low ERA’s and extremely high spin rates.

b4 <-
  read.csv('b4June1.csv')
b4
b4gr <-
  b4 %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = velocity, y = spin_rate, color = total_pitches)) +
  geom_point(stat = 'identity') +
  xlab('Velocity (mph)') +
  ylab('Spin Rate (rpm)') +
  ggtitle('Spin Rate VS Velocity Prior to June 1st')

p1 <-
  ggMarginal(b4gr, type = 'histogram')
